data.description: Come fall in love with this beautiful end-unit townhome in Chesapeake. Lower level includes a walk-out finished rec room and 1-car garage. Main level features a eat-in Kitchen,with a balcony off the back of the home with views of the Elizabeth City River. The kitchen has a large island then opens onto a Living Room with a conveniently placed powder room. Espresso cabinets throughout, granite counter tops and LVP flooring. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms with ample closet space, a hall bath & convenient laundry closet. Owner’s Bedroom features a tray ceiling and walk -in closet. A separate Owner’s Bath features a dual vanity & shower. Community has a private pool & clubhouse.
